title: For Sale/Trade:  Mossberg S51M Mannlicher Stock 22lr
postcontent: Fairly rare Mossberg & Sons S51M Mannlicher stock semiautomatic 22lr rifle. The "S" indicates that this was one of the special manufacturing runs for Spiegel catalog, made in the late 1930's and early 1940's. These are neat older rifles, and have some interesting features.
